            <section xml:id="d0/d84/class_app_store_1_1_common_1_1_suspension_manager_1ae4db8757e5db7b1dbeaf095646a88484">
                <title>static async Task AppStore.Common.SuspensionManager.SaveAsync ()</title> <emphasis>&lt;summary&gt;
Save the current &lt;see cref=&quot;SessionState&quot;/&gt;.</emphasis>
                
<para>Any Frame instances registered with <link linkend="d0/d84/class_app_store_1_1_common_1_1_suspension_manager_1ae3bdf40f19a04f7807435d79c501e91f">RegisterFrame</link> will also preserve their current navigation stack, which in turn gives their active <link linkend="db/d2f/class_page">Page</link> an opportunity to save its state. </para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>An asynchronous task that reflects when session state has been saved.</para>
</formalpara>
</para>

